_pdbx_database_remark.id     285 
_pdbx_database_remark.text   
;THE ENTRY COORDINATES 
ARE NOT PRESENTED IN THE STANDARD CRYSTAL FRAME

IN ORDER TO GENERATE THE CRYSTAL AU, APPLY THE
FOLLOWING TRANSFORMATION MATRIX OR MATRICES AND SELECTED
BIOMT RECORDS TO THE COORDINATES, AS SHOWN BELOW.
X0  1    1.00000    0.00010   0.00000   -0.37209 
X0  2   -0.00010    1.00000   0.00052   -0.40208
X0  3   -0.00000   -0.00052   1.00000   -41.34830
CRYSTAL AU =
(X0) * CHAINS A and B
;
# 
